      "text": "（いよいよ本番だ。すずの出番は一瞬だけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It's finally the real thing. Suzu's scene is just a moment‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7917574406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.3527937412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、周りは一流の役者さんばかり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Everyone around me is such a skilled actor…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3527937412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.7696642558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私はただ、映り込むだけですのに\nどうしてこんなに緊張するんですの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just supposed to appear on screen‚ but…\nWhy am I so nervous…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6671929359,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3986.1852963000006,
          "startTime": 21.6533782322
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5093.820794399999,
          "startTime": 22.7610137303
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.0958545048
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.4990947724
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.6942675273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（すず、右手と右足が同時に出てるぞ　）\n（なんとか緊張をほぐせないだろうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Suzu‚ your right hand and right foot moved at the same time…）\n（How can I help her relax…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3005262692,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4029.9767972,
          "startTime": 29.3305030664
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9338596026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……。全然ダメですわ……\nさすがの私もへこみますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… I messed up.\nEven I'm getting discouraged.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5987395922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すず、固くなり過ぎだぞ\nどうしたんだ。練習ではちゃんと出来ていたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ you're getting too tense.\nWhat's wrong? You were able to do it during practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1654062588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.7320729255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "練習の時は、{user}さんだけでしたから\n意識しなかったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During practice‚ it was just you‚ {user}-san‚ that's why…\nI didn't have to think about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3987395922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "実際に現場に来たら、有名な監督さんや\n役者さんばかりで……頭が真っ白に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ at the actual shoot‚ there's the famous director\nand other actors…My mind goes blank…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4320729255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ立っているだけですのに\nもう十回もNGを出してしまいましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just standing here‚ but…\nI've already given ten NGs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "周囲のスタッフさんや役者さんもイライラし出して\n私なんか外せと言う方も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even the staff and other actors are getting frustrated…\nSome are even suggesting that I be replaced…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことまで言われたのか！？\nちょっと待っててくれ、俺が掛け合ってくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did they really say that?!\nHold on a moment‚ let me talk to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、その方のおっしゃることはもっともです\n次のシーンの撮影だってありますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ what they're saying makes sense.\nWe have more scenes to shoot after this one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "私を外して撮影を続けた方が\n撮影現場のためになると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would benefit the shoot more\nif they continue without me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ、映り込むだけですし\n他の方に替えていただいても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ I'm just supposed to be in the background…\nThey could replace me with someone else…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、それでいいのか？\nあんなに練習してきたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is that really okay?\nAfter practicing so hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "……仕方ありませんわ\nこれ以上、みなさまに迷惑は掛けたくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I have no choice.\nI don't want to inconvenience everyone any further.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……すずがそう言うなら、無理強いはしない\nでも俺は悔しい。すずだってそうじゃないのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If Suzu says so‚ I won't force you.\nBut I feel frustrated. Aren't you‚ too‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "大した役じゃなくても、沢山悩んで、練習してきただろ\nすずはこの役を誰よりも理解してるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it's not a significant role‚ you've thought and practiced a lot.\nYou should understand this role better than anyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "女優としてのすずが見たい。俺は本気でそう思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to see the actress Suzu. I genuinely think that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ですが私、どうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But how can I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
